heroSlider v0.1a

This is currently an alpha version of the plugin and should be considered unusable until
a beta version is released.

Keep an eye on this page for a usable build.

Planned Features:

Customize Scrolling Times:
    Delay for each slide
    Auto-scroll timeout
    Auto-scroll disable
    Pause on hover disable

Customizable Transitions:
    Choose from default transitions for all slides
    Use different transitions for each slide with data-attributes
    
Visuals:
    Automatically added buttons and "jump-to" bars
    Simple to modify css for customizing buttons
    Enable or disable jump to slide bar
    Allow next / previous slides to be previewed
    Responsive Sizing for hero unit
    Caption support and customizability
